title: Guitars that ate my brain -Full CD rip-
description:
A compilation CD with many talented guitarists.  If you like guitar shredding, then this is for you.  Perfectly melodic in every aspect.  I purchased this album, and I want you all do to the same if you like these artists.  Enjoy!  This is a real gem!  especially the Dave Martone song!

Gigsta

Tracks -

1. Boot Dagger Boogie - Paul Waggoner
2. The life and Times of Sir Walker Sickert - Kris Norris
3. Hybrid Angels - Dave Martone
4. Disengaged - Ron thal (AkA Bumblefoot)
5. The Unwavering Collapse - Eyal Levi, Emil werstler
6. Artichoke Samurai - Shane gibson
7. Nerd alert - Devin Townsend
8. L.D.E. - Chris Poland
9. Hydra - Ola Frenning, Christofer Malmstrom
10. Stomped - Mike Orlando
11. Maiden Voyage - James Murphy
12. Shrodinger's Cat Paradox - Hugues Lefevere, Yann Mouhad
